# Tomato and Egg Stir Fry

## Ingredients
- 2 tomatoes
- 3 eggs
- 1 tablespoon oil
- 1 teaspoon salt
- 1 teaspoon sugar
- 2 tablespoons water

## Instructions
1. Cut the tomatoes into small pieces.
2. Beat the eggs in a bowl.
3. Heat oil in a pan and cook the eggs first, then remove them.
4. Add the tomatoes and cook until soft.
5. Add salt, sugar, and water.
6. Put the eggs back into the pan and stir together.
7. Serve hot with rice.

## Notes
This is a simple homemade dish and one of my favorite comfort foods.